Description: Astrocast SA, formerly known as ELSE SA, is a Switzerland-based company, which is primarily engaged in the aerospace industry. The Company operates as a provider of a network of nanosatellites that are used in machine-to-machine (M2M) services. The Company's solutions help in fleets and remote objects management. It's products include Astronode DevKit, which securely connects clients assets to the Astrocast nanosatellite network; Astronode S is a bidirectional solder-down module for customers wanting a simple serial interface connection to Astrocast network using small size allows for its use in embedded applications that works in all weather conditions; Astropreneur Program advanced global nanosatellite IoT network to tackle challenges in industries such as Agriculture & Livestock, Oil, Gas & Mining, Maritime, Environmental, Connected Vehicles, and IoT (Internet of Things) Devices.
